# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:50
translate spanish tammybuy_5fe05401:

    # "Tammy walks over to the coffee maker and starts making my order, giving me little glances the whole time."
    "Tammy se acerca a la cafetera y empieza a prepararme lo que he pedido, lanzándome pequeñas miradas todo el rato."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:52
translate spanish tammybuy_9d092198:

    # "Then when it's ready, she brings it over and hands it to me with a smile."
    "Luego, cuando está listo, me lo trae y me lo entrega con una sonrisa."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:53
translate spanish tammybuy_bcf489e2:

    # tm "There you go. Hope you like it. Come back and see me soon, okay?"
    tm "Toma. Espero que te guste. Vuelve a verme pronto, ¿vale?"

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:54
translate spanish tammybuy_ce85c25e:

    # pc "I definitely will."
    pc "Sin duda lo haré."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:55
translate spanish tammybuy_5232ddb1:

    # "With that, I take my drink and head out."
    "Con eso, cojo mi bebida y me voy."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:58
translate spanish tammybuy_a4155248:

    # "I nearly drink the whole thing as I drive over to school."
    "Me lo bebo casi todo mientras conduzco hacia la escuela."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:68
translate spanish suzybuy_59e438d3:

    # ss "I'm not interested in talking to you right now, [bro]."
    ss "Ahora mismo no me apetece hablar contigo, [bro]."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:69
translate spanish suzybuy_c5ff5a75:

    # pc "I just wanted to order a--"
    pc "Solo quería pedir un..."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:70
translate spanish suzybuy_9b09fef9:

    # ss "Just leave me alone."
    ss "Déjame en paz."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:71
translate spanish suzybuy_350e21a3:

    # pc "Okay, sorry."
    pc "Vale, lo siento."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:72
translate spanish suzybuy_c5cf0c4b:

    # "I leave the cafe. Hopefully she gets over her anger soon. I'm not really sure what I can do about it."
    "Salgo de la cafetería. Espero que se le pase el enfado pronto. No sé muy bien qué puedo hacer al respecto."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:75
translate spanish suzybuy_41b9410d:

    # "Suzy is working, but she just looks at me angrily when I start to approach the counter."
    "Suzy está trabajando, pero se limita a mirarme con enfado cuando me acerco al mostrador."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:76
translate spanish suzybuy_75c50bfb:

    # "She's obviously still mad at me. I should try to talk to her at home sometime to see if we can patch things up."
    "Está claro que sigue enfadada conmigo. Debería intentar hablar con ella en casa algún día para ver si podemos arreglar las cosas."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:77
translate spanish suzybuy_2ad9f9e9:

    # "For now, I'll just leave."
    "Por ahora, me voy."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:82
translate spanish suzybuy_ca9233d4:

    # ss "Okay [bro], I'll make it, just one sec."
    ss "Vale, [bro], ya lo preparo, un momento."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:84
translate spanish suzybuy_9c865c74:

    # "It doesn't take her long to make my drink and hand it over to me with a smile."
    "No tarda mucho en prepararme la bebida y entregármela con una sonrisa."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:85
translate spanish suzybuy_46f91cfe:

    # ss "Let me know if it's good. I'm still not really sure what I'm doing back here."
    ss "Dime si está bueno. Todavía no tengo muy claro qué hago aquí."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:86
translate spanish suzybuy_ebec7bc6:

    # pc "Okay, [sis]. See you later."
    pc "Vale, [sis]. Nos vemos luego."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:88
translate spanish suzybuy_0274819f:

    # ss "Bye, [bro]."
    ss "Adiós, [bro]."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:89
translate spanish suzybuy_5232ddb1:

    # "With that, I take my drink and head out."
    "Dicho esto, cojo mi bebida y me voy."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:91
translate spanish suzybuy_39cfe670:

    # "The coffee isn't as good as when Tammy makes it. I think Suzy must have mixed something wrong."
    "El café no está tan bueno como cuando lo hace Tammy. Creo que Suzy debe de haber mezclado algo mal."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:93
translate spanish suzybuy_4aa8e188:

    # "Still, it's not bad and I finish most of it on the way to school."
    "Aun así, no está mal y me lo termino casi todo de camino al colegio."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:105
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_5486d453:

    # "When I walk into Java Lava, there is a different person there. Instead of Suzy or Tammy, an older man stands behind the counter."
    "Cuando entro en Java Lava, hay otra persona allí. En lugar de Suzy o Tammy, hay un hombre mayor detrás del mostrador."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:108
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_f8f1fc53:

    # "Man" "Hello there young man, welcome to Java Lava."
    "Man" "Hola, joven, bienvenido a Java Lava."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:109
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_e704be14:

    # "Man" "Can I get you anything?"
    "Man" "¿Te puedo traer algo?"

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:110
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_aa4dec1c:

    # pc "Are you new? I've never seen you here before."
    pc "¿Eres nuevo? No te había visto aquí antes."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:111
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_8aa532ea:

    # "Man" "Ha ha, no I'm actually the owner of Java Lava."
    "Man" "Ja, ja, no, en realidad soy el dueño de Java Lava."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:112
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_492b8d66:

    # "Man" "I don't work the counter very often since I have the girls to do that."
    "Man" "No suelo trabajar en el mostrador muy a menudo, ya que tengo a las chicas para hacerlo."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:113
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_7298db2f:

    # "Man" "Most of the time, I'm stuck in the back doing paperwork, but Tammy is taking weekends off now, so I'm filling in up here."
    "Man" "La mayor parte del tiempo estoy encerrado en la trastienda haciendo papeleo, pero ahora Tammy se toma los fines de semana libres, así que la sustituyo aquí."

# game/Locations/javalava.rpy:114
translate spanish mrmcgeebuy_0a460fcb:

    # mrmg "My name is Mr. McGee, nice to meet you."
    mrmg "Me llamo Sr. McGee, encantado de conocerte."

